{"name": "python3-cyberfusion-yavb", "metadata": {"name": "python3-cyberfusion-yavb", "version": "1.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["semver", "typer", "tomlkit"], "summary": "Version bumper for software projects.", "upload_time": 1733327878}, "documentation": ["# python3-cyberfusion-yavb\n\nYAVB is a CLI tool to bump versions and update changelogs.\n\nSupported systems:\n\n* PyProject (Python)\n* Debian\n\nIt was built by Cyberfusion with two main purposes:\n\n- Automatically bump SemVer version for multiple projects in bulk\n- Bump versions for multiple systems simultaneously (e.g. Python packages distributed on PyPI **and** as Debian packages)\n\n# Install\n\n## Debian\n\nRun the following commands to build a Debian package:\n\n    mk-build-deps -i -t 'apt -o Debug::pkgProblemResolver=yes --no-install-recommends -y'\n    dpkg-buildpackage -us -uc\n\n## PyPI\n\nRun the following command to install the package from PyPI:\n\n    pip3 install python3-cyberfusion-yavb\n\n# Configure\n\nNo configuration is supported.\n\n# Usage\n\nAll examples assume that your projects are in the directory `projects/`.\n\n## Example: increment patch (SemVer) for PyProject\n\n```bash\nyavb --system pyproject \\\n  --bump patch \\\n  --directory projects/your-project/ projects/other-projects/*/\n```\n\n## Example: increment minor (SemVer) for Debian and PyProject, on Debian\n\n```bash\nyavb --system debian --system pyproject \\\n  --bump minor \\\n  --directory projects/your-project/ projects/other-projects/*/ \\\n  --changelog 'Make this project great again' \\\n  --name 'John Doe' \\\n  --email 'john@example.com'\n```\n\n## Example: increment minor (SemVer) for Debian, on non-Debian\n\nChanging Debian packaging requires Debian, which you can run inside a Docker container.\n\nBuild the Docker container:\n\n```bash\ndocker build -t yavb-local .\n```\n\nRun the Docker container:\n\n```bash\ndocker run --rm -t -v $(pwd)/projects/:/projects -w /projects yavb-local \\\n  yavb \\\n  --system debian \\\n  --bump minor \\\n  --directory your-project/ other-projects/*/ \\\n  --changelog 'Make this project great again'\n  --name 'John Doe' \\\n  --email 'john@example.com'\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "cyberfusion.YAVB.systems", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "cyberfusion.YAVB.systems.System", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "cyberfusion.YAVB.systems.System.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "directory", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Set attributes."]}, {"name": "cyberfusion.YAVB.systems.System.version", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Get current version."]}, {"name": "cyberfusion.YAVB.systems.System.update", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "version", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "changelog_entry", "type": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "full_name", "type": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "email_address", "type": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Update system (version, changelog, etc.)"]}], "class_variables": [], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": ["